data.description: Feel at home in this spacious two-level w/ attached garage. Open space on the bottom floor has an integrated kitchen w/quartz counter, dining area & living room, making for fantastic household social area. The large bedrooms are perfect for a little privacy when needed. Hardwood floors throughout most of home. Two walk-in closets! The primary bedroom also features a bath with double sinks, standing shower w/ low step-in & soaking bathtub for relaxation. A little aesthetic work makes this otherwise plug & play home a win! Nestled comfortably on a quiet road in a highly desired area between Fredrickson and South Hill, this home is near several main arterial roads providing convenient access to nearby facilities and JBLM.
